headline: AZZ (AZZ) Misses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: AZZ (AZZ) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -0.64% and -2.84%, respectively, for the quarter ended August 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
